<Base title="Community Guidelines — Pickup">
  <h1>Community Guidelines</h1>
  <p><em>Draft — finalize before store submission (PLAN.md §8).</em></p>
  <ul>
    <li>Be who you say you are. No impersonation or fake skill ratings.</li>
    <li>Show up when you join. Repeated no-shows may limit your account.</li>
    <li>No harassment, hate, or unwanted contact — on courts or in chat.</li>
    <li>Report anything unsafe. Reports are reviewed within 24 hours, and moderation always comes with a stated reason and an appeal path.</li>
    <li>Blocking someone makes you mutually invisible everywhere: events, chat, and live check-ins.</li>
  </ul>
</Base>
